Two Dashboard Views
GigShield has two distinct dashboard experiences: one for workers and one for insurers/admins.

Worker Dashboard
Purpose
Give the worker a clear, at-a-glance view of their protection status, recent claims, and earnings protected — in under 5 seconds of screen time.
